		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform" ><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=59305"><span id=Sage>Fennyin</span></a><b><span id=Sage><br>Sage</span></b><br><img src=/shared/user_star_ico.gif height=9 width=9><br>147 posts
		   <br><nobr><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [4.60]</nobr><br><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Fennyin&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>I can't say I'm absolutely sure of this, but I think your formula for haste is wrong.&nbsp;&nbsp;What I've seen is:<br><br>Attacks Per Second (with no haste) = 10 / Delay <br>Delay (with no haste) = 10 / Attacks Per Second<br><br>since each &quot;point&quot; of delay is about 1/10 of a second<br><br>Attacks Per Second (with haste) = (10 / Delay) * (1 + Haste%)<br><br>for example, multiply by 1.21 for 21% haste<br><br>So, new delay = 10 / ((10 / Delay) * (1 + Haste%))<br><br>Which simplifies to 1 / ((1 / Delay) * (1 + Haste%))<br><br>There's also a damage calculator thread over at Paladins of Norrath: <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showMessage?topicID=13787.topic<br><br><em" target=_new>http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showMessage?topicID=13787.topic<br><br><em</a> id=fs8>Edited, Thu Feb  7 11:45:40 2002</em></p><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Impresario Dennovin Donnovin, Half Elf Maestro<br>Sir Fennyin Ellies, High Elf Lord Protector<br>The Arisen, Terris-Thule</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >0 Replies</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><tr><td class=mhback align=right><span class=mh id=fs8><a class=mh href=/db/classes.html?class=6><img src=/shared/root_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="Up" width=17 height=11> Thread Index</a> |  <a class=mh href=/db/classes.html?class=6&post=1><img src=/shared/new_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="New" width=17 height=11> New Subject</a> | <a 